@startuml
title SupportBot - System Context

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 90
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #4b5563
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #1f2937
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #f8fafc
skinparam PackageBorderColor #1f2937
skinparam PackageBackgroundColor #eef2ff
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #1f2937
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #ecfeff
skinparam ActorBorderColor #1f2937
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #fef3c7

actor "Telegram User" as TelegramUser
actor "Support Manager" as SupportManager
rectangle "Telegram Bot API" as TelegramApi
rectangle "Supabase Realtime\nWebSocket" as SupabaseRealtime
rectangle "OpenAI API\nembeddings + responses" as OpenAiApi

package "SupportBot" as SupportBot {
  rectangle "support-admin\nNext.js admin dashboard" as SupportAdmin
  rectangle "Knowledge Base admin APIs\n/api/kb/* + /api/clients/*" as AdminApi
  rectangle "telegram-webhook\nSupabase Edge Function" as TelegramWebhook
  database "Supabase Postgres\nclients, messages, managers,\nclient assignments, read states,\nteam chat, manager statuses,\nknowledge base, ai usage,\nai reply events" as SupportDb
}

rectangle "Supabase Platform" as SupabasePlatform

TelegramUser --> TelegramApi : sends support\nmessage
TelegramApi --> TelegramWebhook : forwards webhook\nupdate
TelegramWebhook --> SupportDb : upserts client,\nstores inbound message,\nupdates workflow status,\nAI eligibility and timestamps
TelegramWebhook --> OpenAiApi : creates embeddings\nand formats answer
TelegramWebhook --> SupportDb : searches KB,\nstores ai_bot message,\nai usage and ai events
TelegramWebhook --> TelegramApi : sends greeting,\nAI answer or fallback

SupportManager --> SupportAdmin : opens dashboard,\nworks with dialogs
SupportAdmin --> SupportDb : reads dialogs,\nworkflow status,\npriority, assignee,\nteam chat and KB data
SupportAdmin --> AdminApi : sends admin actions\n(status, priority,\nassignment, KB reindex)
AdminApi --> SupportDb : updates chat state,\nmanual priority and KB data
AdminApi --> OpenAiApi : creates KB embeddings\nfor reindexing

SupportDb --> SupabaseRealtime : emits table\nchange events
SupabaseRealtime --> SupportAdmin : pushes realtime\nupdates

TelegramWebhook --> SupabasePlatform : deployed on
SupportAdmin --> SupabasePlatform : uses project URL,\nauth session and realtime
AdminApi --> SupabasePlatform : uses manager session
SupportDb --> SupabasePlatform : hosted by
OpenAiApi --> SupabasePlatform : external AI provider

@enduml
